# Previous npm pack artifacts — never recursively include these (they
# would double the tarball size and ship a stale .amxd from the previous
# release). See 2026-04-14 incident where 1.10.5.tgz initially contained
# both 1.10.5 and 1.10.4 copies of the .amxd via recursive inclusion.
livepilot-*.tgz
